subSections.title: Glyph origin
subSections.text: Unorthodox variant of {{l|zh|巢}} found in a {{w|Movable type#Metal movable type in China|moveable type}} copy of ''{{w|Biographies of Exemplary Women}}'' 《{{w2|zh|列女傳}}》. First attested in 《{{w2|zh|宋元以來俗字譜}}》, a {{w|Variant Chinese character|variant forms}} dictionary compiled in 1930 that records unorthodox forms ({{l|zh|俗字}}) that have existed since the {{w|Song dynasty}}.
